summary:
this is one of my 1st mods for skyrim. CONTAINS: full forge equipment set.
im still a little sloppy. but we all start somewhere ;)
descriptionHtml:
This expansion contains a full forging area in a new part of the home that merges seamlessly and contains well placed lighting. I\'m currently working on adding some extra features to help make the home even preferred place to live in Skyrim.
